TextEng: You gots to explain yourself.
Text: 너 설명해야 해.

TextEng: You will have to explain yourself, Desther.
Text: 데스터, 설명해야 할 거야.

TextEng: What about Fenthick? Yous evil stuff may gets him doomed, too.
Text: 펜딕은 어떻게 되고? 너 나쁜 짓 때문에 그 사람도 망할 수 있어.

TextEng: What about Fenthick? Your trickery may damn him, too.
Text: 펜딕은 어떻게 되지? 네 속임수로 그도 파멸할 수 있어.

TextEng: That enough, me take yous back to Neverwinter right nows!
Text: 이제 됐어, 나 너 지금 당장 네버윈터로 데려가!

TextEng: Enough! I'm taking you back to Neverwinter right now!
Text: 됐어! 지금 당장 네버윈터로 데려가겠어!

TextEng: You shut up. Me gonna look around here before taking yous back.
Text: 입 닥쳐. 나 너 데려가기 전에 여기 좀 둘러볼 거야.

TextEng: Shut up. I'm going to look around this place before I take you back.
Text: 입 닥쳐. 너를 데려가기 전에 이곳을 좀 둘러볼 거야.

TextEng: Me gots other questions, now.
Text: 나 지금 다른 질문 있어.

TextEng: I have other questions I need to ask.
Text: 물어볼 게 좀 더 있어.

TextEng: Why Neverwinter attacked? Why you spread plague?
Text: 왜 네버윈터 공격당했어? 왜 너 역병 퍼뜨렸어?

TextEng: Why was Neverwinter attacked? Why did you spread the plague?
Text: 왜 네버윈터가 공격당한 거지? 왜 역병을 퍼뜨린 거야?

TextEng: Yous explain! What the plague do?
Text: 너 설명해! 역병이 뭐 했어?

TextEng: Explain what you mean! What did the plague do?
Text: 설명해 봐! 역병이 뭘 한 거야?

TextEng: If yous not start plague, who did?
Text: 너 역병 시작 안 했으면, 누가 했어?

TextEng: If you did not start the plague, who did?
Text: 네가 역병을 시작하지 않았다면, 누가 한 거지?

TextEng: Who you follow?
Text: 너 누구 따라?

TextEng: Who are your masters?
Text: 네 주인은 누구지?

TextEng: How many of yous is there? How many "Eye People" you got?
Text: 너희 몇 명이야? "눈동자 교단" 몇 명 있어?

TextEng: How big is your group? How many "People of the Eye" are there?
Text: 조직이 얼마나 커? "눈동자 교단"이 몇 명이나 되지?

TextEng: You tells what Old Ones is! You tell now!
Text: 너 태고의 존재들이 뭔지 말해! 지금 말해!

TextEng: What are the Old Ones! Tell me!
Text: 태고의 존재들이 뭐야! 말해 봐!

TextEng: Where the cure?
Text: 치료법 어디 있어?

TextEng: Where is the cure?
Text: 치료법은 어디 있지?

TextEng: Me should just kills you right now.
Text: 나 지금 당장 너 죽여야 해.

TextEng: I should end your life right now.
Text: 지금 당장 네 목숨을 끝내야겠어.

TextEng: Yous gonna be taken to get judged.
Text: 너 심판받으러 갈 거야.

TextEng: You will be taken back to face judgment.
Text: 심판을 받으러 돌아가게 될 거야.
